data.description: Masimo is looking for summer interns to join our Software Engineering team. We value all of our interns and go the extra mile to make sure you receive a learning experience that fits your career goals. You will become knowledgeable in your assigned area. You will also learn how to work in a professional environment and have ample opportunity to network with department leaders and other employees in the organization. Job Summary: These positions will support phases of the software development lifecycle for our current portfolio and upcoming product releases.
